text: Ernie Nunn (23 September 1904 – 11 September 1991) was a former Australian rules footballer who played with Footscray and Collingwood in the Victorian Football League (VFL). == Notes == == External links == * *Ernie Nunn's profile at Collingwood Forever Category:1904 births Category:1991 deaths Category:Australian rules footballers from Victoria (Australia) Category:Western Bulldogs players Category:Collingwood Football Club players
